OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779376270
OL,3,CUK sends #20m to Congo as Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak grows
OL,6,FThe UK is sending #20m to help contain
OL,7,Fan outbreak of Ebola in the Democratic
OL,8,FRepublic of the Congo and Uganda as
OL,9,Fhealth workers struggle to fight the
OL,10,Frare variant of the illness that has
OL,11,Fkilled more than 130 people.
OL,13,FCongolese authorities said they had
OL,14,Frecorded almost 600 suspected cases
OL,15,Fand 139 suspected deaths from the
OL,16,Fvirus, and the World Health
OL,17,FOrganisation (WHO) suggested the
OL,18,Foutbreak could last for at least two
OL,19,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779376270
OL,3,CUK sends #20m to Congo as Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak grows
OL,6,FThe WHO has deemed the outbreak a
OL,7,Fpublic health emergency of
OL,8,Finternational concern, but assessed
OL,9,Fthe risk it will spread globally as
OL,10,Flow.
OL,12,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,13,F"It is vital we act now to save lives
OL,14,F` outbreaks like Ebola do not stop at
OL,15,Fborders, and neither can we."
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779376270
OL,3,CUK sends #20m to Congo as Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak grows
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,7,Fhas activated its "returning workers
OL,8,Fscheme" to monitor those travelling
OL,9,Ffrom the UK to the area for work, and
OL,10,Fis assessing routes that travellers
OL,11,Fuse to enter the UK to ensure
OL,12,Finformation on Ebola symptoms is
OL,13,Favailable to those who need it.
OL,15,FDr Mike Reynolds, incident director at
OL,16,Fthe UKHSA, said the current outbreak
OL,17,Fwas "serious" but posed a "low" risk
OL,18,Fto the UK population.
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@GO]yD@EOUyD@MO]yD@[OUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
