FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779376270
OL,3,CUK sends #20m to Congo as Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak grows
OL,6,FEbola is a rare, highly contagious and
OL,7,Foften fatal disease generally
OL,8,Ftransmitted via bodily fluids.
OL,10,FSymptoms include a high temperature,
OL,11,Fextreme tiredness, vomiting,
OL,12,Fdiarrhoea, muscle pain and bleeding.
OL,14,FThe outbreak has been made worse by
OL,15,Finstability in the region, local
OL,16,Fleaders said. An attack by militants
OL,17,Flinked to the Islamic State group
OL,18,Fkilled at least 17 people on Tuesday
OL,19,Fnight in Alima village in Ituri, a
OL,20,Fprovince that has become the hot spot
OL,21,Fof the outbreak.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779376270
OL,3,CUK sends #20m to Congo as Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak grows
OL,6,FTons of health supplies have been
OL,7,Fairlifted to Bunia, where the first
OL,8,Fknown death was announced last week,
OL,9,Fbut residents said masks are harder to
OL,10,Ffind and some disinfectants that
OL,11,Fpreviously sold for 2,500 Congolese
OL,12,Ffrancs (about 75p) now cost four times
OL,13,Fmore.
OL,15,FThe rare type of Ebola, known as the
OL,16,FBundibugyo virus, spread undetected
OL,17,Ffor weeks following the first known
OL,18,Fdeath while authorities tested for
OL,19,Fanother, more common Ebola virus and
OL,20,Fcame up negative.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
