FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779376270
OL,3,CUK sends #20m to Congo as Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak grows
OL,6,FSo far, 51 cases have been confirmed
OL,7,Fin Congo's northern provinces of Ituri
OL,8,Fand North Kivu, and two cases in
OL,9,FUganda, WHO Director-General Tedros
OL,10,FAdhanom Ghebreyesus said on Wednesday.
OL,11,FThere are 139 suspected deaths and
OL,12,Falmost 600 suspected cases.
OL,14,FBut "the scale of the epidemic is much
OL,15,Flarger," he said.
OL,26,@vD@EOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779376270
OL,3,CUK sends #20m to Congo as Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak grows
OL,6,FThe London-based MRC Centre for Global
OL,7,FInfectious Disease Analysis estimated
OL,8,Fthat cases have been substantially
OL,9,Fundercounted and that the actual
OL,10,Fnumber could already exceed 1,000.
OL,11,F"The true magnitude remains
OL,12,Funcertain," it said.
OL,14,FThis is Congo's 17th Ebola outbreak,
OL,15,Fand the WHO has said the country's
OL,16,Fhealth ministry has experienced staff
OL,17,Fand capacity to respond. Most
OL,18,Foutbreaks, however, were of the more
OL,19,Fcommon Ebola type.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
