OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779376270
OL,3,CUK sends #20m to Congo as Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak grows
OL,6,FOutbreaks of the disease occur
OL,7,Fperiodically in Africa, with the most
OL,8,Fsevere taking place in West Africa
OL,9,Fbetween 2014 and 2016 and leading to
OL,10,Fmore than 11,000 deaths.
OL,12,FThat outbreak also saw three British
OL,13,Fnationals ` two nurses and an aid
OL,14,Fworker ` contract the disease.
OL,16,FAll three survived, and there have
OL,17,Fbeen no cases of human-to-human
OL,18,Ftransmission in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
