FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779376270
OL,3,CUK sends #20m to Congo as Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak grows
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a US national who tested
OL,7,Fpositive in Congo arrived in Berlin on
OL,8,FWednesday and was in a special
OL,9,Fisolation ward where a "comprehensive
OL,10,Fexamination" was underway, German
OL,11,FHealth Ministry spokesperson Martin
OL,12,FElsasser said.
OL,14,FAnd a top health official in the Czech
OL,15,FRepublic said they are receiving an
OL,16,FAmerican doctor who was treating Ebola
OL,17,Fpatients in Uganda and who is without
OL,18,Fsymptoms.
OL,26,@tD@Dxp
